Class LibraryResource

java.lang.Object
LibraryResource
Direct Known Subclasses:
ElectronicResource, PhysicalResource
class LibraryResource extends Object
Represents a library resource both physical and electornic. This class servers as a base for PhysicalResource and ElectronicResource classes.
